name: 💥 Farmer 🌽 Violet ⭐ Carter

name: 💥 Farmer 🌽 Violet ⭐ Carter
description: Vi • Anti-War ☭ Commie • 🐑 Farmer • Disabled • 💕Married to @Carterforva   •🤰👶 • #ActuallyAutistic • ADHD • EDS🦓 • Non-Binary • They/Them • DONATE ⬇️
tweet: @Only_More_So So I learner early on to be grateful that I "wasn't autistic" because that would be "bad and wrong" bc that's what the trusted adults in my life said. 🥲 turns out they just actually hated me for who I was the whole time.

name: 💥 Farmer 🌽 Violet ⭐ Carter
description: Vi • Anti-War ☭ Commie • 🐑 Farmer • Disabled • 💕Married to @Carterforva   •🤰👶 • #ActuallyAutistic • ADHD • EDS🦓 • Non-Binary • They/Them • DONATE ⬇️

My family vehemently didn't believe in autism, and made a point of very loudly protesting any time someone brought it up. They acted so spooked, I assumed it must be bad.

name: 💥 Farmer 🌽 Violet ⭐ Carter
description: Vi • Anti-War ☭ Commie • 🐑 Farmer • Disabled • 💕Married to @Carterforva   •🤰👶 • #ActuallyAutistic • ADHD • EDS🦓 • Non-Binary • They/Them • DONATE ⬇️
tweet: Oh. And normalize and embrace neurodiversity. That's the bare minimum.

name: 💥 Farmer 🌽 Violet ⭐ Carter
description: Vi • Anti-War ☭ Commie • 🐑 Farmer • Disabled • 💕Married to @Carterforva   •🤰👶 • #ActuallyAutistic • ADHD • EDS🦓 • Non-Binary • They/Them • DONATE ⬇️
tweet: What we can do is validate self diagnoses, knowing that there are racial, class, and gender factors that deny many folks to that "fair" diagnostic access, and be open & supportive by listening & sharing their content. Anything more? Ask them. That's a great start.

name: 💥 Farmer 🌽 Violet ⭐ Carter
description: Vi • Anti-War ☭ Commie • 🐑 Farmer • Disabled • 💕Married to @Carterforva   •🤰👶 • #ActuallyAutistic • ADHD • EDS🦓 • Non-Binary • They/Them • DONATE ⬇️
tweet: That said, I do NOT reach out to non-white folks who may be on the spectrum, publicly, ever. The non-white experience of autism has a history of trauma & violence, that runs as old and deep as most of the racial transgressions we've committed. It doesn't feel like my place/lane.

name: 💥 Farmer 🌽 Violet ⭐ Carter
description: Vi • Anti-War ☭ Commie • 🐑 Farmer • Disabled • 💕Married to @Carterforva   •🤰👶 • #ActuallyAutistic • ADHD • EDS🦓 • Non-Binary • They/Them • DONATE ⬇️
tweet: When autism has been the WHITE, MALE diagnoses for literal decades.. MAYBE ITS TIME to unpack the ableism, and start being inclusive, honest with ourselves, and open minded.

name: 💥 Farmer 🌽 Violet ⭐ Carter
description: Vi • Anti-War ☭ Commie • 🐑 Farmer • Disabled • 💕Married to @Carterforva   •🤰👶 • #ActuallyAutistic • ADHD • EDS🦓 • Non-Binary • They/Them • DONATE ⬇️
tweet: So when I tell you women & nonbinary afab folks, and BIPOC folks deserve support and information they've been denied, I mean it. Please don't get defensive at the suggestion that maybe your brain is a little bit like mine. 😬

name: 💥 Farmer 🌽 Violet ⭐ Carter
description: Vi • Anti-War ☭ Commie • 🐑 Farmer • Disabled • 💕Married to @Carterforva   •🤰👶 • #ActuallyAutistic • ADHD • EDS🦓 • Non-Binary • They/Them • DONATE ⬇️
tweet:
Today, medical diagnoses is restrictive by class and resources, so often even when these programs exist to help neurodivergent students, BIPOC groups are more frequently denied the privelege of diagnoses than yt ppl, and thus to those programs.
Add on the societal stigma...

name: 💥 Farmer 🌽 Violet ⭐ Carter
description: Vi • Anti-War ☭ Commie • 🐑 Farmer • Disabled • 💕Married to @Carterforva   •🤰👶 • #ActuallyAutistic • ADHD • EDS🦓 • Non-Binary • They/Them • DONATE ⬇️
tweet: White autistic kids who they felt "functioning" enough went to gifted programs. Black & brown kids, and poor yts went to special ed, or down the school to prison pipeline. Special education was literally only created to continue racial segregation.

name: 💥 Farmer 🌽 Violet ⭐ Carter
description: Vi • Anti-War ☭ Commie • 🐑 Farmer • Disabled • 💕Married to @Carterforva   •🤰👶 • #ActuallyAutistic • ADHD • EDS🦓 • Non-Binary • They/Them • DONATE ⬇️
tweet: The only group more undiagnosed and unsupported are Black, Indigenous, Latine, and other non-white autistic folks. The world is aware of autism, but apparently not of the diverse ways it applies. We should be spreading the real information, which is why I'll always gently inform.

name: 💥 Farmer 🌽 Violet ⭐ Carter
description: Vi • Anti-War ☭ Commie • 🐑 Farmer • Disabled • 💕Married to @Carterforva   •🤰👶 • #ActuallyAutistic • ADHD • EDS🦓 • Non-Binary • They/Them • DONATE ⬇️
tweet: As someone who is ADHD & Autistic... my experience is my own. We are not a monolith... but if I see an opportunity to help someone else avoid that endless feeling like something is WRONG with them, I will.

name: 💥 Farmer 🌽 Violet ⭐ Carter
description: Vi • Anti-War ☭ Commie • 🐑 Farmer • Disabled • 💕Married to @Carterforva   •🤰👶 • #ActuallyAutistic • ADHD • EDS🦓 • Non-Binary • They/Them • DONATE ⬇️
tweet: Also, I usually only approach women & afab folks on this topic bc we go GROSSLY undiagnosed/misdiagnosed with anxiety disorders, adhd, borderline personality disorder/other personality disorders. ASD was considered a "boy" thing in the 80s & 90s & some docs still think this way.

name: 💥 Farmer 🌽 Violet ⭐ Carter

tweet: I think this is just my autism, because I have never wanted anything enough to hurt someone else for it. I've never felt like my life was worth more than someone else's based on physical differences. I genuinely struggle to understand WHY people do all the shit we do... idk.

name: 💥 Farmer 🌽 Violet ⭐ Carter
description: Vi • Anti-War ☭ Commie • 🐑 Farmer • Disabled • 💕Married to @Carterforva   •🤰👶 • #ActuallyAutistic • ADHD • EDS🦓 • Non-Binary • They/Them • DONATE ⬇️
tweet: And I recently learned HUMANS HAVE STRIPES that are just on a frequency of light we can't see. My point here is... all we see is what we CAN see. The whole picture is often hidden... so it seems so strange to me that we chose PIGMENT to discriminate over. Like. What are we doing?

name: 💥 Farmer 🌽 Violet ⭐ Carter
description: Vi • Anti-War ☭ Commie • 🐑 Farmer • Disabled • 💕Married to @Carterforva   •🤰👶 • #ActuallyAutistic • ADHD • EDS🦓 • Non-Binary • They/Them • DONATE ⬇️
tweet: Literally, the phenomenon of color is subjective. I have EXTRA cones in my eyes, so I can see colors some folks can't. My ex spouse? Green Blue colorblind. Animals see different frequencies of light than we do. Antelope can't see orange, so tigers, bright orange, are "invisible"

name: 💥 Farmer 🌽 Violet ⭐ Carter

tweet: Human biology is so cool and magical, and here we are hung up on the most arbitrary, unimportant things we could possibly be hung up on. I've struggled to understand my whole life how we got here, and it finally has sunk in that its always been about control. 😕

name: 💥 Farmer 🌽 Violet ⭐ Carter
description: Vi • Anti-War ☭ Commie • 🐑 Farmer • Disabled • 💕Married to @Carterforva   •🤰👶 • #ActuallyAutistic • ADHD • EDS🦓 • Non-Binary • They/Them • DONATE ⬇️
tweet: It starts feeling fake after awhile. Like maybe you are just telling yourself you've healed a ton of stuff... so when it starts showing profits in your life, it ALWAYS feels a little surreal, bc surely it couldn't be that simple. Surely TRAUMA couldn't be THAT influential.😅🤯

name: 💥 Farmer 🌽 Violet ⭐ Carter
description: Vi • Anti-War ☭ Commie • 🐑 Farmer • Disabled • 💕Married to @Carterforva   •🤰👶 • #ActuallyAutistic • ADHD • EDS🦓 • Non-Binary • They/Them • DONATE ⬇️
tweet: I hope it is real. I hope it lasts. It seems like an impossible thing, for them to come back now, truly repentant. I'm beside myself. Isn't this the ideal situation you could ever dream of when confronting parental childhood trauma? Like. This is good, right? What the hell?🤣

name: 💥 Farmer 🌽 Violet ⭐ Carter
description: Vi • Anti-War ☭ Commie • 🐑 Farmer • Disabled • 💕Married to @Carterforva   •🤰👶 • #ActuallyAutistic • ADHD • EDS🦓 • Non-Binary • They/Them • DONATE ⬇️
tweet: But I have to wonder just a little bit if I set this in motion. I hope so. It would mean that putting in the work to heal ur traumas, personal & generational, can have a positive ripple effect in ur life/the lives of people u love, by giving the same grace u gave/give urself.

name: 💥 Farmer 🌽 Violet ⭐ Carter
description: Vi • Anti-War ☭ Commie • 🐑 Farmer • Disabled • 💕Married to @Carterforva   •🤰👶 • #ActuallyAutistic • ADHD • EDS🦓 • Non-Binary • They/Them • DONATE ⬇️
tweet: So. I KNOW they can change. I WANT them to be free from their traumas and to learn/heal, but the lizard in my brain that fears them because they failed the little girl they made? 🥲 I want to trust them, half believe they can't change, and I'm afraid of how much I need them to.😅

name: 💥 Farmer 🌽 Violet ⭐ Carter
description: Vi • Anti-War ☭ Commie • 🐑 Farmer • Disabled • 💕Married to @Carterforva   •🤰👶 • #ActuallyAutistic • ADHD • EDS🦓 • Non-Binary • They/Them • DONATE ⬇️
tweet: Neuroplasticity is a thing, and basically it means you CAN heal & recover from almost any trauma. You CAN recover from the worst humans can offer, because I did. It wasn't even hard once I figured out I was stuck in a cycle of abuse & revictimization, and became trauma informed.

name: 💥 Farmer 🌽 Violet ⭐ Carter
description: Vi • Anti-War ☭ Commie • 🐑 Farmer • Disabled • 💕Married to @Carterforva   •🤰👶 • #ActuallyAutistic • ADHD • EDS🦓 • Non-Binary • They/Them • DONATE ⬇️
tweet: Maybe seeing me cut every single family member off, cold, and leave empowered them. Especially when I did not fail & come running back to them. I healed & they saw me change for the better. Maybe they want that too. The clinical side of me knows there's time for them to change.

name: 💥 Farmer 🌽 Violet ⭐ Carter
description: Vi • Anti-War ☭ Commie • 🐑 Farmer • Disabled • 💕Married to @Carterforva   •🤰👶 • #ActuallyAutistic • ADHD • EDS🦓 • Non-Binary • They/Them • DONATE ⬇️
tweet: I've waffled back & fourth on the why or how of it. The traumatized part of me wants not to trust it, but my logical & informed mind knows that I have it in me to give them the grace to try, and even to fail if they need to. Maybe they are healing now, because I broke the cycle?

name: 💥 Farmer 🌽 Violet ⭐ Carter
description: Vi • Anti-War ☭ Commie • 🐑 Farmer • Disabled • 💕Married to @Carterforva   •🤰👶 • #ActuallyAutistic • ADHD • EDS🦓 • Non-Binary • They/Them • DONATE ⬇️
tweet: Most shockingly, my MOM recently got back in contact with me, and is entering the first stages of repair like my dad did a year ago. I still have a ton of pain & anger, but I have to admit & recognize the rare gift I've received. How is it that both of my parents are healing NOW?

name: 💥 Farmer 🌽 Violet ⭐ Carter

tweet: Because he seems truly committed to building new trust and repairing trauma he caused, that means I have the rare opportunity to enforce anti-racism, anti-ableism, anti-fascist, etc boundaries with him, beyond the general emotional & interpersonal stuff. So I will.

tweet: I don't know if my brain does this to protect me, or if it's something I chose. I don't know what the end stages of healing are supposed to look like. Now my life is all live, all the time... and as scary as that is, because now I feel like I have everything to lose... I'm happy.

name: 💥 Farmer 🌽 Violet ⭐ Carter
description: Vi • Anti-War ☭ Commie • 🐑 Farmer • Disabled • 💕Married to @Carterforva   •🤰👶 • #ActuallyAutistic • ADHD • EDS🦓 • Non-Binary • They/Them • DONATE ⬇️
tweet: But it was real. I know it was. Yet in my mind I still think about that scared little girl, who only knew that life. Did I kill her? Did they? Do we bury her together, or do we just let her go? I do not know.

name: 💥 Farmer 🌽 Violet ⭐ Carter
description: Vi • Anti-War ☭ Commie • 🐑 Farmer • Disabled • 💕Married to @Carterforva   •🤰👶 • #ActuallyAutistic • ADHD • EDS🦓 • Non-Binary • They/Them • DONATE ⬇️
tweet: And the thing that makes it seem so far away and not real, is how very real and attached I feel NOW. A life masking my autism left me with very little of me that came from ME. I didn't feel like a whole person until I was 30. Like I was in product demo mode for 29 fucking years.

name: 💥 Farmer 🌽 Violet ⭐ Carter

tweet: And it was a shitty show, that I kept asking myself why I was still watching. And then I forget about it. And then something reminds me, and I'm back there for a minute, in my own private showing of something that doesn't feel like it belongs to me.
